*Current workaround*: This can be fixed with a find and replace over the space import XML as follows:

{noformat}
abc123.atlassian.net (old URL)

with

123abc.atlassian.net (new URL)
{noformat}
and
{noformat}
d8f6e739-950c-3ee9-b9c6-e65a0c0486e6 (old application link ID)

with

047ba870-a006-3434-afd1-6d18ea1b8174 (new application link ID)
{noformat}

Then perform the space import again with your new file.

