Space label is deprecated starting from Confluence 5 and later.

Some organizations were using this feature heavily before and probably had some in house macros that utilizes this feature.

Upgrading Confluence to v5 will break things. Shall we consider the option to migrate space label to space category instead?

h5. Workaround:
This query will migrate existing labels from space label to space category (backup the DB first!):
{code}
UPDATE label SET NAMESPACE = 'team' WHERE LABELID IN (SELECT LABELID FROM content_label l JOIN CONTENT c ON l.CONTENTID = c.CONTENTID WHERE c.CONTENTTYPE = 'SPACEDESCRIPTION') AND NAMESPACE = 'global'; 
{code}

